<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Backend Geliştirme Sınavı | İçerik Yönetim Sistemi</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #6366f1;
      --secondary: #a5b4fc;
      --accent: #fbbf24;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --text: #1e293b;
      --card-bg: #fff;
      --shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
      --radius: 1.5rem;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .navbar {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
      padding: 1.2rem 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .navbar .brand {
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-right: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .navbar .menu {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .navbar .menu a {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
      position: relative;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    }
    .navbar .menu a::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--primary);
      transition: width 0.3s;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .navbar .menu a:hover {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    .navbar .menu a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .hero-header {
      width: 100vw;
      margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1 60%, #a5b4fc 100%);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 0 0 2rem 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(99,102,241,0.10);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s;
    }
    .hero-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .hero-header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #e0e7ef;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .exam-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .question {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .question h3 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .options {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .option {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .option:hover {
      background: #f1f5f9;
      border-color: var(--primary);
    }
    .option input[type="radio"] {
      width: 1.2rem;
      height: 1.2rem;
    }
    .submit-btn {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .submit-btn:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="/" class="brand"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> İçerik Yönetim Sistemi</a>
    <nav class="menu">
      <a href="/">Ana Sayfa</a>
      <a href="/dersler">Dersler</a>
      <a href="/katilimcilar">Katılımcılar</a>
      <a href="/denemeler">Denemeler</a>
      <a href="/hakkimda">Hakkımda</a>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-header">
    <h1>Backend Geliştirme Sınavı</h1>
    <p>Node.js, API, sunucu ve backend teknolojileriyle ilgili 15 soruluk deneme</p>
  </div>

  <div class="exam-container">
    <form id="examForm">
      <div class="question">
        <h3>1. Node.js'de asenkron işlemler nasıl yönetilir?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q1" value="a">
            <span>a) Callback fonksiyonları</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q1" value="b">
            <span>b) For döngüleri</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q1" value="c">
            <span>c) While döngüleri</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q1" value="d">
            <span>d) If-else yapıları</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>2. REST API'de HTTP metodlarından hangisi veri güncellemek için kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q2" value="a">
            <span>a) GET</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q2" value="b">
            <span>b) POST</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q2" value="c">
            <span>c) PUT</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q2" value="d">
            <span>d) DELETE</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>3. Express.js'de middleware nedir?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q3" value="a">
            <span>a) Veritabanı bağlantısı</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q3" value="b">
            <span>b) İstek ve yanıt işleme katmanı</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q3" value="c">
            <span>c) Frontend framework</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q3" value="d">
            <span>d) Web sunucusu</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>4. MongoDB'de bir koleksiyondan veri silmek için hangi metod kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="a">
            <span>a) find()</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="b">
            <span>b) insert()</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="c">
            <span>c) deleteOne()</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q4" value="d">
            <span>d) update()</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>5. JWT (JSON Web Token) ne için kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="a">
            <span>a) Veri şifreleme</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="b">
            <span>b) Kimlik doğrulama</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="c">
            <span>c) Dosya sıkıştırma</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q5" value="d">
            <span>d) Veri sıkıştırma</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>6. Node.js'de process.env ne için kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q6" value="a">
            <span>a) Çevre değişkenlerine erişim</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q6" value="b">
            <span>b) Dosya sistemi işlemleri</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q6" value="c">
            <span>c) Ağ bağlantıları</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q6" value="d">
            <span>d) Veritabanı işlemleri</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>7. Express.js'de route parametreleri nasıl tanımlanır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="a">
            <span>a) /:parametre</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="b">
            <span>b) /parametre</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="c">
            <span>c) /?parametre</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="d">
            <span>d) /#parametre</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>8. MongoDB'de $lookup operatörü ne için kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="a">
            <span>a) Veri silme</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="b">
            <span>b) Koleksiyonlar arası join</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="c">
            <span>c) Veri güncelleme</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="d">
            <span>d) Veri ekleme</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>9. Node.js'de Promise nedir?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q9" value="a">
            <span>a) Asenkron işlem sonucu</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q9" value="b">
            <span>b) Senkron işlem</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q9" value="c">
            <span>c) Veritabanı bağlantısı</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q9" value="d">
            <span>d) Web sunucusu</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>10. Express.js'de app.use() ne için kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q10" value="a">
            <span>a) Middleware eklemek</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q10" value="b">
            <span>b) Route tanımlamak</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q10" value="c">
            <span>c) Veritabanı bağlantısı</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q10" value="d">
            <span>d) Web sunucusu başlatmak</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>11. MongoDB'de $group operatörü ne için kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q11" value="a">
            <span>a) Veri gruplama</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q11" value="b">
            <span>b) Veri silme</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q11" value="c">
            <span>c) Veri ekleme</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q11" value="d">
            <span>d) Veri güncelleme</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>12. Node.js'de process.nextTick() ne için kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q12" value="a">
            <span>a) Bir sonraki event loop iterasyonunda çalıştırma</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q12" value="b">
            <span>b) Asenkron işlem</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q12" value="c">
            <span>c) Senkron işlem</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q12" value="d">
            <span>d) Web sunucusu</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>13. Express.js'de res.json() ne için kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q13" value="a">
            <span>a) JSON yanıtı göndermek</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q13" value="b">
            <span>b) HTML yanıtı göndermek</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q13" value="c">
            <span>c) Dosya göndermek</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q13" value="d">
            <span>d) Veritabanı işlemi</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>14. MongoDB'de $match operatörü ne için kullanılır?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q14" value="a">
            <span>a) Veri filtreleme</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q14" value="b">
            <span>b) Veri ekleme</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q14" value="c">
            <span>c) Veri silme</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q14" value="d">
            <span>d) Veri güncelleme</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question">
        <h3>15. Node.js'de EventEmitter nedir?</h3>
        <div class="options">
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q15" value="a">
            <span>a) Olay tabanlı programlama</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q15" value="b">
            <span>b) Veritabanı işlemi</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q15" value="c">
            <span>c) Web sunucusu</span>
          </label>
          <label class="option">
            <input type="radio" name="q15" value="d">
            <span>d) Dosya sistemi</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Sınavı Tamamla</button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('examForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      // Burada sınav sonuçlarını işleyebilirsiniz
      alert('Sınav tamamlandı! Sonuçlarınız değerlendiriliyor...');
